Assignment report link:

www.cse.iitb.ac.in/~prasanth/cg_a21


KEYBOARD BINDINGS of the robot:

Esc : close window

g : single key Robot-Vehicle transformations

V : rotate X clockwise
v : rotate X counter-clockwise
B : rotate Y clockwise
b : rotate Y counter-clockwise
N : rotate Z clockwise
n : rotate Z counter-clockwise

Z : tilt head to robot's right
z : tilt head to robot's left
X : tilt head forward
x : tilt head back
C : look to robot's left
c : look to robot's right

T : bend forward
t : bend back

A : robot's right shoulder down
a : robot's right shoulder up
S : robot's right shoulder clockwise
s : robot's right shoulder counter-clockwise
D : robot's right shoulder back
d : robot's right shoulder forward
F : robot's right elbow clockwise
f : robot's right elbow counter-clockwise

Q : robot's left shoulder down
q : robot's left shoulder up
W : robot's left shoulder clockwise
w : robot's left shoulder counter-clockwise
E : robot's left shoulder back
e : robot's left shoulder forward
R : robot's left elbow clockwise
r : robot's left elbow counter-clockwise


H : robot's right leg to left
h : robot's right leg to right
J : robot's right leg backward
j : robot's right leg forward
K : robot's right leg counter-clockwise
k : robot's right leg clockwise
L : robot's right knee bend
l : robot's right knee straighten

U : robot's left leg to left
u : robot's left leg to right
I : robot's left leg backward
i : robot's left leg forward
O : robot's left leg counter-clockwise
o : robot's left leg clockwise
P : robot's left knee bend
p : robot's left knee straighten
